docs {
  # Send Prompt
  
  Send a prompt to an existing chat window.
  
  ## Path Parameters
  - `terminalId` (string): Terminal ID (format: tmux-{sessionName}:{windowIndex})
  
  ## Request Body
  - `prompt` (string, required): The prompt to send
  - `delay` (number, optional): Delay in ms before sending (default: 500)
  
  ## Response
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "terminalId": "tmux-mobile-project:1",
    "message": "Prompt will be sent to the chat window"
  }
  ```
}
